      "text": "[REDACTED] stated she believed these objects to have been platter shaped rather than b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "spherical and to have been considerably larger than an airplane of the cub",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
