      "text": "type which was flying in a different portion of the sky at the same time.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "She advised that these objects appeared to her to be at a great distance",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "and constructed of some white metallic material.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
