      "text": "[REDACTED] attention was first drawn to the objects by an ex-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "planation from one of the children to the effect that the airplane was sky-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "writing. The objects were grouped in approximately an arc about level with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "the sun and to the left of the sun as viewed by [REDACTED]. They did not",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "change positions during the 3 or 4 minutes which she observed them but some b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "of the larger of the objects appeared to rotate rapidly in the manner of a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
